                ----------
                to add acpid event handling:
                1. Add event capture file to /usr/local/etc/acpi/events
                2. Add script to /usr/local/etc/acpi/actions
                ----------
                to control acpid:
                $ sudo /usr/local/etc/init.d/acpid [start|stop|restart|status]
                ----------
                to trouble-shoot
                $ sudo acpid -dfl
